  "remarks": "TAi.031 Title: a) Mullah b) Haji. Designation: a) President of Central Bank (Da Afghanistan Bank)under the Taliban regime b) Minister of Finance under the Taliban regime. Believed to be in Afghanistan/Pakistan border area. Belongs to Kakar tribe. He is a member of the Taliban Supreme Council. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 1822 (2008) was concluded on 23 Jul. 2010.; Listing: Listed by UN 1267 Committee on 23 February 2001 (amended on 21 Sep 2007, 29 Nov. 2011 and 31 Dec. 2013)",
